{"tid":897041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"奶頭髮","createTime":"2018-11-10T14:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T14:29:49.000Z","uid":221092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53db8ea8565279cd1bfadcf1e4da06f80d3ff589","tid":897041,"uid":221092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:29:49.000Z","msg":"有網民在Facebook群組「爆料公社」貼文稱，其女友周三（7日）在雲林縣斗六市遇到一名變態男子。當時其女友搭𨋢期間，該男子稱她頭上有蜘蛛，並說可幫忙捉拿，其女友不虞有詐，結果對方撥弄頭髮一番後，又稱蜘蛛跑到頭髮裏，要求她蹲下。雖然女友感覺不妥，但礙於𨋢內只有他們2人，只好依對方所說。<br />\n<br />\n該男子同晚故技重施，在𨋢內對另一女子下手。從閉路電視畫面所見，他不斷把玩女子的頭髮，而且身體靠得很近，並狂舐女子的頭髮，之後還追她出𨋢。隨後該女子發現頭髮沾有不明黏液，慌忙致電向朋友求救及報警。面對警員問話，該男子堅稱自己沒有不當行為，只是幫忙捉蜘蛛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}